{{TagLine|AC1600 Wi-Fi Range Extender}} :{{ProductPage|http://www.tp-link.com/us/products/details/RE400.html}}{{SupportPage|vendor=TP-LINK|model=RE400}} *Web GUI: http://tplinkrepeater.net Most of the information on this page was copied from the [[TP-LINK RE450]] since the FCC ID is the same. This router appears to be a stripped down RE450 [[List of Costco Exclusive Wireless Devices|exclusively for Costco]]. Netgear only claims 300 Mbps 802.11n speeds for the RE400 but it's not clear if they have actually reduced the capabilities or if this is just a marketing change.
